      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Meticulously maintained and presented in showroom condition, it offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning collector. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care rarely seen in the pre-owned market. We invite you to experience this exceptional example of engineering excellence.",
