    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem and it\u2019s honestly in pristine, showroom-level shape. It\u2019s been babied since day one\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection! It drives like a total dream and still has that wonderful fresh car feel. I'm looking for someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
