    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute gem: a 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman in pristine Guards Red. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and shows like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professionally applied ceramic coating. Inside, the black leather interior remains supple and scent-free, with absolutely no bolster wear or creasing on the seats. Every button, dial, and technological feature functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history documented exclusively at authorized Porsche centers and only 12,000 original miles. The 19-inch Boxster S wheels are immaculate, without a single instance of curb rash, and are wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands a vehicle in showroom-new state. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
