      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty\u2014it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s in absolutely stunning shape inside and out. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel. I'm looking for a great new home for it where it'll be just as loved. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
