    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours condition. This chassis features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that pulls cleanly to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is equipped with a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. To ensure mechanical longevity, the rod bearings have been replaced and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced\u2014essential for maintaining structural rigidity under high-load cornering. The suspension remains taut with refreshed OEM bushings, and the cross-drilled rotors provide immediate, fade-free deceleration. The exterior finish is flawless, showing zero oxidation or swirl marks, making this a turn-key specimen for the discerning purist.",
